*Subject:* Request for Guidance on GSoC 2025


I’m Akanksha Bathla, a developer passionate about open-source contributions and preparing for GSoC 2025. I came across your work on *rdevguide*, and I’m inspired by your contributions.

Could you kindly share insights or suggestions to help me get started and contribute effectively? Any guidance from you would be immensely helpful.

Thank you for your time and support!

Best regards,
Akanksha Bathla
Email: <mailto:akanksha018btcse22@gmail.com|akanksha018btcse22@gmail.com>
